000100*****************************************************************         
000200*                                                                         
000300*   KOHL'S BITMAP MANIPULATION UTILITY                                    
000300*   THIS CONTAINS THE PARAMETERS NEEDED TO CALL THE BITMAP                
000300*   MANIPULATION UTILITY 'DPKUT170'.                                      
000400*                                                                         
000400*                                                                         
000500*****************************************************************         
000500 01  DP170-PARAMETERS.                                                    
000500     05  DP170-BYTE                 PIC  X(01).                           
000500     05  DP170-BITS                 PIC  X(08).                           
000500     05  FILLER  REDEFINES  DP170-BITS.                                   
000500         10  DP170-BIT-TABLE        OCCURS 8 TIMES                        
000500                                    INDEXED BY DP170-BT-IDX.              
000500             15  DP170-BIT          PIC  X(01).                           
000500     05  DP170-ACTION-CODE          PIC  X(01).                           
000500         88  DP170-AC-DISPLAY-BITS               VALUE 'D'.               
000500         88  DP170-AC-CHANGE-BITS                VALUE 'C'.               
000500     05  DP170-RETURN-CODE          PIC S9(08)   COMP SYNC.               
000500         88  DP170-RC-OK                         VALUE +0.                
000500         88  DP170-RC-ERROR                      VALUE +4000,             
000500                                                       +4001,             
000500                                                       +4002,             
000500                                                       +4003.             
000500         88  DP170-RC-MISSING-PARMS              VALUE +4000.             
000500         88  DP170-RC-INVALID-ACTION-CODE        VALUE +4001.             
000500         88  DP170-RC-INVALID-BITS               VALUE +4002.             
000500         88  DP170-RC-INVALID-CHANGE             VALUE +4003.             
